# Phase 3 & 4 Implementation Plan

This plan documents the strategy for integrating the backend API with the Admin Dashboard logic, as well as the newly requested MVP Voice & Accessibility features for the Clerk journey.

## User Review Required

> [!WARNING]
> Please review this plan carefully as we are implementing the final API hooks for Admin configuration and jumping right into the complex Voice integration involving the Web Speech APIs.

## Proposed Changes

### 1. Phase 3: Admin Integration 

The Admin interface currently pulls from hardcoded mocks. We will dynamically string these to the `/v1/admin` FastApi router endpoints.

#### [MODIFY] [admin/page.tsx](file:///c:/PaperTrail_Colohacks/frontend/src/app/admin/page.tsx)
- Fetch `GET /v1/admin/documents/latest` rather than `mockRecentUploads` to view recent documents scanned by clerks across the system.
- Map the endpoint's response elements representing `clerk_uid`, `template_name`, and `submitted_at` into the global oversight table.

#### [MODIFY] [admin/users/page.tsx](file:///c:/PaperTrail_Colohacks/frontend/src/app/admin/users/page.tsx)
- Pull all system users from `GET /v1/admin/users`.
- Wire the "Promote" and "Demote" buttons cleanly to `PATCH /v1/admin/users/{uid}/role`.

#### [MODIFY] [admin/templates/pending/page.tsx](file:///c:/PaperTrail_Colohacks/frontend/src/app/admin/templates/pending/page.tsx)
- Replace pending queue mocks with `GET /v1/admin/templates/pending`.
- Attach `POST /v1/admin/templates/{id}/approve` to the Approve actions.
- Attach `POST /v1/admin/templates/{id}/reject` (taking the reason payload) into the rejection modal.

#### [MODIFY] [admin/records/page.tsx](file:///c:/PaperTrail_Colohacks/frontend/src/app/admin/records/page.tsx)
- Provide access to all historical records via `GET /v1/admin/records`.

